      \ the sequence we can write in this loop\n            chunk_size = min(remaining,\
      \ self.length - self.idx)\n            \n            # Write the chunk to the\
      \ output buffer\n            out[out_idx:out_idx + chunk_size] = self.seq[self.idx:self.idx\
      \ + chunk_size]\n            \n            # Update pointers and counters\n\
      \            self.idx = (self.idx + chunk_size) % self.length\n            out_idx\
      \ += chunk_size\n            remaining -= chunk_size\n            \n       \
      \ return n_output\n"
